    <chapter xml:id="sec-itemref-property-values">
        <title>Spine <markup>itemref</markup> Properties</title>

        <para>The following tables define properties for use in the <olink targetdoc="packages" targetptr="sec-itemref-elem"
                type="epub-spec">itemref element</olink>
            <olink targetdoc="packages" targetptr="attrdef-itemref-properties" type="epub-spec">properties
            attribute</olink>.</para>

        <para>The <emphasis role="strong">Cardinality</emphasis> field indicates the number of times the property <literal
                role="rfc2119">must</literal> appear within the Package Document scope, and the <emphasis role="strong"
                >Usage</emphasis> field indicates usage conditions.</para>

